Omega Pharma Spends 17.4 Million Euros on Additional Buybacks

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-09-21T16:38:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/omega-pharma-spends-17-4-million-euros-on-additional-buybacks.html
Omega Pharma (OME)  NV said it spent
almost 17.4 million euros buying back an additional 502,906 own
shares in on- and off-market transactions in the period from
Sept. 13 through Sept. 21, according to an e-mailed statement.  Omega Pharma held 10 percent of its outstanding share count
following the transactions, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  